query:
INSERT INTO streaming_id_mappings (tmdb_id, watchmode_id, media_type)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                ON CONFLICT (tmdb_id)
                DO UPDATE SET 
                    watchmode_id = EXCLUDED.watchmode_id,
                    media_type = EXCLUDED.media_type,
                    last_verified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                    updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
